+# Prebuilt (IMPORTED) FidelityFX libraries can't be install(TARGETS)/exported —
+# they're DELAYLOAD'd into the rexruntime shared lib, so only the DLL needs to
+# ship. Install those as files; build-in-tree targets go through install(TARGETS).
